videos.headline: Nebraska strikes first with 16-yard passing TD
videos.description: Adrian Martinez finds Omar Manning for a 16-yard touchdown, giving the Cornhuskers the early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Omar Manning scores 16-yard Receiving touchdown vs. Purdue) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue's defense comes up big with 45-yard pick-six
videos.description: Purdue's LB Jalen Graham takes it 45 yards the other way for a Boilermakers touchdown.

videos.headline: Nebraska reclaims the lead with 4-yard rushing TD
